g.title: get_user_input
g.text: Get coordinates and years for predicting the model from the web app user.

g.title: extract_prism_data
g.text: Load the prism data file with precipitation values and extract the data for the input coordinates and save as a csv file.

g.title: gen_paleocar_model
g.text: generate paleocar models for predicting the climate for the given years.

g.title: exrtact_prediction_model
g.text: extract the rasterbrick reconstruction from a PaleoCAR batch model for the specified prediction period.

g.title: extract_uncertainty_model
g.text: extract the LOOCV uncertainty information from the set of Paleocar models for specified period.
